{
  "title": "Garden-fresh Canadian Potatoes Pilaf",
  "description": "A light and airy pilaf featuring charlotte potatoes, fresh herbs, and a touch of monsoon-inspired spices. Perfect for a weeknight dinner or a summer evening.",
  "cuisine": "Canadian",
  "diet": [
    "vegetarian",
